{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-11808/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-11808"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:18:08"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["overhead"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Man's purple socks in bed, woman gripping his foot"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-11808","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-11808"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1/69d5b6cb-e4e9-46fb-af83-69e97d52a820","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:38:53.770Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds’s colorful socks, one of the first images associated with the dressmaker, provide a pop of color in an otherwise cold exterior. Here, Alma covers them as if she is tucking in her sick child. Much as when she offers to drive for Reynolds, she continues taking control.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:535.4986760812004,66.3548102383053,887.1315092674316,951.5269196822595"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1/501c5d5e-6284-4703-808d-29809784246c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:39:25.469Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>While before Reynolds had resisted Alma’s attempts to take care of him, here he finally submits to her ministrations. There is a maternal bent to her caretaking—she takes off his shoes as a mother would for her child who had not yet learned to dress himself. This is where his complete return to a childish state begins.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11808/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:62.70079435127979,96.01059135039712,219.45278022947923,192.33892321270963"}}}]}]}]}